    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEARCH ALL - STEAMPUNK</h2> is a game in the genre of &quot;hidden object&quot;, in which you need to find all the bolts and screws on a large location drawn in the style of &quot;doodling&quot;. The location depicts a steampunk-style town. In the foreground of the location there are unusual houses, such as crab houses, a mill house and a house of unknown purpose. In the middle of the city, along its entire length, there is a stone bridge for transport, cars and carts move along it. In the sky, a cyber owl sits on steam pipes, blinking constantly. There are also several &quot;Heavenly towns&quot; in the sky.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br>- Animation elements on location;<br>- &quot;Doodling&quot; design style;<br>- 80 bolts/screws to be found;<br>- Pleasant soundtrack:<br>- The gameplay can be interrupted at any time, and the game will automatically save the result.",
